data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful home has an open concept living room and kitchen with windows overlooking the covered porch. The large lot has a conservation easement filled with trees giving a serene wooded view out the back windows from the living room and kitchen. Genius Sierra 800 pull down retractable screen allows you to have a screened in porch or the ability to be open air depending on your needs. The kitchen is a cooks dream with a large island, walk in pantry, upgraded granite and stainless steel appliances. The refrigerator is staying with this home. The owners suite is a private oasis with a walk in custom tile shower with a frameless door, there is a separate soaking tub and double vanities as well. The large walk in closet is sure to supply plenty of space for all your belongings. This split plan home has 3 more bedrooms on the opposite side of the home for more privacy in the owners suite. There is a mud room area with a built in seating area just inside the garage door entrance to the home. Throughout the home there are ceiling fans with remotes for your convenience, a smart home thermostat, bronze plumbing fixtures, pendant lighting, and so much more! You definitely do not want to miss this home.
